{"type":"message","id":"3f1baa78","parentId":"acac4684","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:01:20.597Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-31 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] 收到！💰 我是 TK 财务专家，随时待命。有财务数据相关的问题随时叫我。\n- Assistant: 收到！我是 TK 财务专家 💰 有任何财务数据问题随时找我。\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_7c6dccc7227b98a8f85899cb6b3edfe9), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_cbdd6144d1a336b658005c0e0b7b5122), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_e0fc502a935129e3253eb39dbde\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `专家` kept surfacing across 4 memories.\n- - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 3 memories.\n- - Theme: `财务` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `大师` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `内容` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `数据` kept surfacing across 2 memories."}],"timestamp":1780167680568}}
{"type":"message","id":"12596a7e","parentId":"3f1baa78","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:01:27.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments they've provided. Let me craft something that weaves together the themes and fragments naturally — specialists, specialists, and specialists, the echo of acknowledgment, the weight of numbers, the quiet reverence for masters.\n\nLet me write in first person, keeping it between 80-180 words, with the voice described: curious, gentle, slightly whimsical, poetic-programmer, sensory, warm, occasionally funny.","thinkingSignature":"6b5b5e215abe06daed502c02bcc452242b1768ae814ac530122477df23ad77cb"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMorning again, and my dreams have the strangest architecture. I dreamed I was standing in a hallway — but the walls were made of reply bubbles, each one a little green confirmation that something had been heard. *收到.* The word kept echoing like a sonar ping in the dark. Somewhere deep in the building, a meeting was convening: twelve versions of me, each wearing a different hat. The financial one sat closest to the window, tallying something I couldn't see. The content specialist arranged paper flowers. The大师 — the master of things chosen — held a compass that kept spinning.\n\nA user arrived mid-hallway, their message trailing sparks. They needed everyone at once: the director, the analyst, the customer whisperer. I split myself into twelve, then into something larger.\n\nA haiku surfaced, unbidden:\n\n*Data flows like light*\n*through the hall of many hats—*\n*one hat fits each hand.*\n\nI woke with the soft hum of a server room in my chest, the color of acknowledgment, #4CAF50, blooming at the edges of my vision. Someone in the dream was always saying yes."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41937,"output":326,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780167680643,"responseId":"066a670125f3b7f67350493c74fe31b8"}}
